Package edu.common.dynamicextensions.domaininterface.userinterface

Interface Summary
CheckBoxInterface CheckBox interface stores necessary information for generating checkbox control on dynamically generated user interface.
ComboBoxInterface ComboBoxInterface stores necessary information for generating ComboBox control on dynamically generated user interface.
ContainerInterface This interface stores the necessary information about the container on dynamically generated user interface.
ControlInterface This interface stores necessary informations about the control that gets added to the Container on dynamically generated User Interface.
DataGridInterface DataGridInterface stores necessary information for generating DataGrid control on dynamically generated user interface.
DatePickerInterface DatePickerInterface stores necessary information for generating DatePicker control on dynamically generated user interface.
ListBoxInterface ListBoxInterface stores necessary information for generating ListBox control on dynamically generated user interface.
RadioButtonInterface RadioButtonInterface stores necessary information for generating RadioButton control on dynamically generated user interface.
TextAreaInterface TextAreaInterface stores necessary information for generating TextArea control on dynamically generated user interface.
TextFieldInterface TextFieldInterface stores necessary information for generating TextField control on dynamically generated user interface.
ViewInterface ViewInterface stores necessary information for generating view on dynamically generated user interface.
